{"word":"χιών","slug":"χιών","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>χιών</b></el> <el>(χιών, όνος, ἡ,) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>snow</i>, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>; <el>νιφάδες χιόνος</el> <i>snow</i> flakes, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>; <el>χιὼν πίπτουσα</el> <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>; <el>χιόνι κατανίφει</el> <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>snow-water, ice-cold water</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>From Root <el>ΧΙ</el>, <a href='S:confer, compare'>cf.</a> <a href='S:χεῖμα'><el>χεῖμα</el></a>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>hiems.</el>\n"}]}